column5: Saturday , just caught my first ever steel head on a float rod.
Nice fish Devon. You got your first one followed up by your second one Good job !!
thanks and ill be up next weekend, NO HOCKEY lol
I should have your float reel fixed by then
Amazing colors of the fish, keep at it!
GREAT JOB, UR GONNA BE HOOKED FOR LIFE NOW
You schooled us all!  Great job out there and it was great to meet you!

Way to go Devon. I'm hearing about your success from here in Quebec....you're getting famous. I see ChrisK's rod in the background there with a big 5 of Diamonds spoon on it. Maybe you should have a word with him about that eh?
Fantastic fish, man...well done!  One more than I've caught on my centerpin
Well done Devon. Great to meet you this weekend.  Here's another pic of that sweet hen     That's a Kwikfish Roy
Good job man!  Say goodbye to disposable income for life now...lol
ya that was great meeting you and ccmt, gotta get up here again
Good catch,if I didn't have to work for a living!,I tell ya!.
